---
title: Pan-Fried Garlic Butter Chicken Thighs with Chips and Tomato Salad
description: These Pan-Fried Garlic Butter Chicken Thighs are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
